ust one goal: Consume or be Consumed! \n\nPowered by elemental forces and mythical artifacts navigate your way through 3 environments with 30+ rounds each to get through. Will you be able to top the leaderboard for each of these? \n\nTEOC provides\u2026\n\u2022 more than 5 hours of mesmerizing gameplay,\n\u2022 a beautiful minimalist style with ambient adaptive soundtracks,\n\u2022 10+ game mechanics to master,\n\u2022 additional powerups to collect and use across all 90+ rounds\n\u2022 with daily powerup rewards for coming back\n\u2022 to compete on the 3 leaderboards,\n\u2022 increasingly challenging level design all procedurally generated\n\u2022 and seated or standing play options!\n\n\n", "short_description": "Evolve from an atomic state to marine-life in this spatial arcade puzzler with just one goal: Consume or be Consumed! \n\nPowered by elemental forces and mythical artifacts navigate your way through 3 environments with 30+ rounds each to get through. Will you be able to top the leaderboard for each of these? With >5 hours of mesmerizing gameplay, 10+ game mechanics to master and all set in a beautiful minimalist style with ambient adaptive soundtracks, you can enjoy it seated or standing up!\n"}]}, "developer_name": "HEADGEAR GbR", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://headgear.io/legal.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://headgear.io/legal.html#terms", "publisher_name": "HEADGEAR GbR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://headgear.io/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "PUZZLE", "ARCADE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_p